Every day, people in Guangxi must eat #ricenoodles, especially in Nanning, where they have fresh rice vermicelli noodles. It has a slightly sour taste, as the rice undergoes fermentation, resulting in a rich and sour flavor. The cooked noodles are served with crispy lettuce, specially made pickled vegetables, fragrant perilla leaves, and chopped green onions, along with a spoonful of minced meat. You must give it a try!
